    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduo a Cython Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>Cython</application> package provides a compiler for
writing C extensions for the Python language.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

      <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Informao do Pacote</bridgehead>
      <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Transferncia (HTTP): <ulink url="&cython-download-http;"/>
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Transferncia (FTP): <ulink url="&cython-download-ftp;"/>
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Soma de verificao MD5: &cython-md5sum;
          </para>
